    "body": "### Describe your issue\n\nThe project description displayed on PyPI reports that Cython can be installed avoiding compilation running\r\n```\r\npip install Cython --install-option=\"--no-cython-compile\"\r\n```\r\nhowever, `pip` since version does not accept the `--install-option` anymore.\r\n\r\nEven when it did, I believe that the option name was `--install-options`.\r\n\r\nThe documentation reports the same instructions https://cython.readthedocs.io/en/latest/src/quickstart/install.html",
